## How AURORA OS Works

AURORA OS enables access through a progressive, trust-led system lifecycle — designed to be compliant, scalable, and inclusive by default.

### Device Activation
AURORA OS is preloaded on partner-manufactured devices, creating a standardized, secure foundation at the point of distribution.

### Identity Creation
Users onboard through licensed local partners, establishing verified identity with explicit consent and regulatory alignment.

### Progressive Service Access
Financial, health, and commerce services are unlocked incrementally as trust, usage, and reputation develop.

### Trust Accumulation & Growth
Users build digital reputation, qualify for enhanced services, and participate fully in the formal digital economy.
This lifecycle ensures access is earned, trusted, and expanded — protecting users, partners, and regulators while enabling scale.

